WEBVTT

00:02:29.275 --> 00:02:35.105
But the dominance of Android
has led to what I call

00:02:35.129 --> 00:02:37.341
the "digital security divide."

00:02:37.365 --> 00:02:40.350
That is, there is now increasingly a gap

00:02:40.374 --> 00:02:44.499
between the privacy
and security of the rich,

00:02:44.523 --> 00:02:47.293
who can afford devices
that secure their data by default,

00:02:48.036 --> 00:02:49.288
and of the poor,

00:02:49.851 --> 00:02:54.525
whose devices do very little
to protect them by default.

